p. 266</ITEM>
</LIST>
<LIST>
<HEAD>CHAP. XCII.</HEAD>
<ITEM>The conjurer and his a&s;&s;ociate execute a plan of ven|geance
again&s;t certain infidels who pretend to de&s;|pi&s;e
