<P>I therefore re&s;olved within my&s;elf to gratify
my lover's expectation, by eloping, if po&s;&s;ible,
that very night; though the execution of this
plan was extremely difficult, becau&s;e my fa$$er
<PB N="76" REF="81">
was upon the alarm, and my own maid, who
was my bedfellow, altogether in his intere&s;t.
Notwith&s;tanding the&s;e con&s;iderations, I found
