the happine&s;s of every woman whom he chanced
at any time to hand into a coach.</P>
<P>The duche&s;s of&mdash;, who was newly
married to the earl of P&mdash;, a particular friend
of lord W&mdash;m's, carried me to court, and
pre&s;ented me to the queen, who expre&s;&s;ed her ap|probation
of my per&s;on in very particular terms,
and ob&s;erved the &s;atisfaction that appeared in my
