I had the good fortune to &s;ucceed. Mr. B&mdash;
told me, that before he &s;aw me, he heard I was
a f$ol; but finding (as he was plea&s;ed to &s;ay)
that I had been egregiou&s;ly mi&s;repre&s;ented, he
