<P>Finding him&s;elf di&s;appointed in his expecta|tions,
he commenced a law-&s;uit again&s;t lord B&mdash;,
though not for a divorce, as we de&s;ired, but
with a view to reclaim me as his lawful wife.
His lawyers, however, attempted to prove cri|minal
