<P>The joy he felt at this di&s;covery lightened in
his eyes; nor was &s;he able to conceal a certain
alacrity and &s;atisfaction that appeared in her
countenance, when &s;he obtained a di&s;tinct view
of her protector's per&s;on. In &s;hort, &s;he was pre|vailed
