operations for the next occa&s;ion: mean while it
was re&s;olved, that Hadgi &s;hould not only exer|ci&s;e
his own talents, but al&s;o employ inferior
agents, in procuring general intelligence for the
&s;upport of their &s;cheme; that the expence of this
mini&s;try &s;hould be defrayed from the profits of
their profe&s;&s;ion; and the remainder be di&s;tributed
to poor families in di&s;tre&s;s.</P>
