to whom he dictated the following adver|ti&s;ement,
which was immediately in&s;erted in one
of the news-papers: &startq;Any per&s;on po&s;&s;e&s;&s;ed of a
male black cat, with white feet, and a b$$$y tail,
not exceeding the age of two or three years, will
find a purcha&s;er, by carrying it to the &s;ign of the
