<P><PB N="299" REF="302">
Neverthele&s;s, &s;he began to harangue them in
her u&s;ual &s;tile, which was not the milde&s;t &s;ort of
expo&s;tulation; and one of the multitude, who
found means to detach him&s;elf from the general
