the &s;ame in&s;tant of time, upon the con$$$$$d
<PB N="300" REF="303">
ho&s;ier, who finding her&s;elf overwhelmed by &s;uch
a number of animals, which &s;he looked upon as
&s;o many fiends &s;ent to torment her, ran agha&s;t into
the &s;treet with di&s;mal outcries, imploring the a&s;|&s;i&s;tance
