into his hand the adverti&s;ement he had received
from Pickle; which he had no &s;ooner peru&s;ed,
than he produced his own, for the &s;atisfaction of
the other party: &s;o that another gloomy pau&s;e
en&s;ued, at the end of which, each uttered a pro|found
&s;igh, or rather groan, and ri&s;ing up, &s;neak'd
